data.description: Here is your chance for a like new home in a nice development Westfield Lakes! You will love the curb appeal and modern features including an open floor plan from living room to the eat in kitchen.  Recessed lighting, center Island and stainless appliances. Upgraded espresso Cabinets and a tile backsplash have been added to complete the modern look. Eat in kitchen and 1/2 bath on the first floor. Walk out to a concrete patio and lots of backyard space. Large bedroom sizes and master with a walk in closet and private bath. The second floor laundry with washer/dryer included. The basement is roughed in for a full bath if you decide to finish for more space. Easy access to 224 and 71 easy commute to Akron or Cleveland. Boating enthusiasts take advantage of the nearby public boat launch at Chippewa Lake and many more amenities that will be coming soon. Quick close possible!
